@startuml
title C4 Level 2 - Container Diagram (NAPCORE Helpdesk)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #2B5FAB
  FontColor #1F2F4A
  BackgroundColor #F8FBFF
}
skinparam actor {
  BorderColor #2B5FAB
  FontColor #1F2F4A
  BackgroundColor #EAF2FF
}

actor "PTO" as PTO
actor "PTA" as PTA
actor "Developer" as DEV
actor "ITS System Integrator" as INTEGRATOR
actor "Ticketing Agent" as TICKET

rectangle "NAPCORE Helpdesk" as SYSTEM {
  rectangle "Web GUI\n(Container)" as GUI #EAF2FF
  rectangle "Question API / Orchestrator\n(Container)\nFAQ-first, then RAG fallback" as API #DCE9FF
  rectangle "FAQ Service\n(Container)\nApproved FAQ lookup + versions" as FAQ #F0F6FF
  rectangle "Retrieval Service\n(Container)\nEmbedding + vector search" as RETRIEVAL #F0F6FF
  rectangle "Generation & Guardrails\n(Container)\nCitation checks, support checks, abstention" as GUARDRAILS #F0F6FF
  rectangle "Editorial Workflow Service\n(Container)\nDraft/Review/Approve/Publish" as EDITORIAL #F0F6FF
  database "PostgreSQL\n(Data Store)\nFAQ, events, evidence links" as PG #EEF5FF
  database "Vector Index\n(Data Store)\nSource chunk embeddings" as VDB #EEF5FF
  rectangle "Ingestion Worker\n(Container)\nSync + chunk + index" as INGEST #F0F6FF
}

rectangle "Approved GitHub Repositories" as GITHUB
rectangle "LLM Provider API" as LLM

PTO --> GUI : Ask questions
PTA --> GUI : Ask questions
DEV --> GUI : Ask questions
INTEGRATOR --> GUI : Ask questions
TICKET --> GUI : Ask questions

' Top layer: actors arranged horizontally
PTO -[hidden]right-> PTA
PTA -[hidden]right-> DEV
DEV -[hidden]right-> INTEGRATOR
INTEGRATOR -[hidden]right-> TICKET

' Bottom layer: external systems below SYSTEM
SYSTEM -[hidden]down-> GITHUB
GITHUB -[hidden]right-> LLM

GUI --> API : Submit question
API --> FAQ : Try canonical FAQ match
API --> RETRIEVAL : Fallback retrieval request
API --> GUARDRAILS : Grounded generation\nand validation
API --> EDITORIAL : Route low-confidence\nor flagged answers
API --> PG : Store question events\nand outcomes

FAQ --> PG : Read/write FAQ entries\nand versions
RETRIEVAL --> VDB : Query top-k chunks
RETRIEVAL --> PG : Log retrieval events
GUARDRAILS --> LLM : Generate answer from\nretrieved context only
GUARDRAILS --> PG : Write evidence links\nand policy outcomes
EDITORIAL --> PG : Store review decisions
INGEST --> GITHUB : Pull allowlisted sources
INGEST --> VDB : Upsert embeddings
INGEST --> PG : Store source metadata

note bottom of API
Decision policy:
1) FAQ high-confidence -> return canonical answer.
2) Else run retrieval + generation.
3) If evidence insufficient or unsupported claim -> abstain.
end note

note right of LLM
Top layer: Users.
Bottom layer: Approved source repositories and LLM.
end note

@enduml
